/** * Superinterface of {@link SortedMultiset} to introduce a bridge method for * {@code elementSet()}, to ensure binary compatibility with older Guava versions * that specified {@code elementSet()} to return {@code SortedSet}. * * @author Louis Wasserman */
unit.class:
interface
SortedMultisetBridge <
E
>
extends
Multiset <
E
>
{
@ Override
SortedSet <
E
>
elementSet ();
}
